{"type": "article", "id": 61169, "title": "山下智久为日淘公司代言，王者荣耀和周生生跨界推出配饰 | 乙方日报", "description": "这里有营销和营销人的一切", "date": "2019-02-13T05:15:35Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 6546, "name": "外卖"}, {"id": 6974, "name": "酸奶"}, {"id": 30560, "name": "王者荣耀"}, {"id": 738, "name": "麦当劳"}, {"id": 11422, "name": "达能"}], "category": 18, "column": 31, "author": 1480589, "comment_count": 6, "praise_count": 27, "image": "img/article/article_show/20190213123608pk3n8YJrH25QuWND.jpg", "contents": "<h3 nocleanhtml=\"true\">明星又代言了啥</h3><p line=\"4PIJ\"><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzA5ODQxOTM5MQ==&amp;mid=2652035470&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=e85b8c0b880a6ff56a98510989d602f8&amp;chksm=8b77ae5ebc0027481bf326daa29480424bfdd98cc75f6a8c1a88f4396727d62d44fe20b86b0b&amp;mpshare=1&amp;scene=1&amp;srcid=0213IeProBczO27YncVlRjD1&amp;key=22211bbfbb5c89f7dc36add9ca70dc5b6224052e508707e5b74b122180568551c9a95e25914378b43698914f7c9f0cbda9058e8757fe5b8a7a3e24351ef957783728aab17889e83e2e8af0a45340a8bf&amp;ascene=0&amp;uin=MjgzNjA1MjcyMQ%3D%3D&amp;devicetype=iMac+MacBookAir7%2C2+OSX+OSX+10.14+build(18A391)&amp;version=12020010&amp;nettype=WIFI&amp;lang=en&amp;fontScale=100&amp;pass_ticket=%2BPHnYc6qxF%2BO6oD64zysJAMIoOpISiYNOvjZcXldV5MLKUyimzFoSQRtESCWCZo4\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>山下智久成为豌豆公主的代言人，</b></a>豌豆公主是主打日本产品的跨境电商公司。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190213123653iMIpaFeDJQLyvdSt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.365625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>又是跨界</h3><p line=\"03Ze\"><a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/status/4338150225090011?\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>王者荣耀和珠宝品牌周生生跨界合作推出珠宝饰品，</b></a>针对情人节发布了“凤求凰”和“凤凰于飞”情侣款，以游戏人物李白和王昭君皮肤为原型。此外，还有妲己、庄周·鲲和梦奇为原型创作的产品。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190213123718SB021e56f8YduHFX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190213123718ljmhxkfHnodaDcyp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190213123719cANYS5y0DVHIozl9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190213123719DlGoIa59Wc8JSjYE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190213123719nfApHwKMaSvG0WVo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>值得一看的 Case</h3><p line=\"D1G7\"><a href=\"https://lbbonline.com/news/tbwaparis-peers-through-rain-soaked-windows-in-gorgeous-mcdonalds-print-ads/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>麦当劳的新广告宣传外送服务。</b></a>广告透过雨水冲刷玻璃的视角，看到是阴沉沉的天空和建筑物，表达了消费者等待外卖的心情。它是由巴西摄影师 Roberto Badin 拍摄，由于他之前对静物和建筑的出色拍摄而被选择进行合作。创意代理商来自 TBWA 巴黎。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190213123741olR7Sirbxdf8IWMp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190213123741VdgA0NQynODuRi1r.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201902131237410qDIXU6i1RNZLrwb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p line=\"3W1r\">达能为庆祝罐装酸奶诞生 100 周年活动，<a href=\"https://adage.com/creativity/work/danone-century-yogurt/971981\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>在巴黎市中心的街头复制了 20 世纪 50 年代和 60 年代的海报。</b></a>因为存档质量不佳无法打印，在获得原作插画家同意之后，将海报复制展现出来。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190213123805ZGw8pDb4J7sqT9jY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p line=\"cccb\">昨天瑞幸咖啡借北京降雪，<a href=\"https://dwz.cn/p4CVDPkS\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>适时推出“瑞雪 · 见鹿” AR互动游戏。</b></a>消费者扫描咖啡杯身的鹿，能够追踪小鹿在故宫雪地中奔跑的场景。不过前提是手边有一只瑞幸的咖啡杯。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190213123826gfpJMybm5tVQ3DLI.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562081\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190213123826dikV01WcP9ORBbg5.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562081\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201902131238269cxInLYCj3ufp71N.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562081\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><p line=\"3WU5\"><a href=\"https://fx.weico.net/share/57774741.html?weibo_id=4338937541689925\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>青岛啤酒在纽约时装周之际推出“桃园三结义”的桶装啤酒，</b></a>创作灵感来自 20 世纪 30 年代的“桃园结义”广告海报。此外，它还在青岛啤酒博物馆中展出了。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201902131238518iQ3u2XJeZPjbaNv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562793\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190213123851h9vKcqgAERWVDZma.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.225115\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>其他，也很重要</h3><p line=\"z4GE\"><b><a href=\"https://adage.com/article/agency-news/nintendo-taps-initiative-media-agency-u-s/316618/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">IPG的 极致传媒（Initiative）将负责任天堂在美国的媒介代理业务</a>，</b>现在是由阳狮的 Blue 449 代理。根据凯度的统计数据，任天堂 2017 年曾在媒介测量上面花费了约 7380 万美元。</p><p line=\"MsQI\"><a href=\"https://www.adweek.com/agencies/mccann-goes-through-a-round-of-layoffs-in-detroit-following-news-of-general-motors-restructuring/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>不过 IPG 旗下的麦肯在美国底特律地区将裁员100 名甚至更多，</b></a>这是由于客户通用汽车重组，它去年叫停了位于底特律的两个改造项目，最近又裁减了数千个工作职位。而 MRM McCann 和 Commonwealth//McCann 直接负责通用汽车最大品牌雪佛兰的全球网络业务。</p><p line=\"vwqP\"><a href=\"http://www.omnicomgroup.com/newsroom/omnicom-group-reports-fourth-quarter-and-full-year-2018-results/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Omnicom 2018 年第四季度财报发布，</b></a>全球收入和去年同期相比下降 2.2%，为 40.9 亿美元。不过有机增长 3.2%，抵消了收入下降。其中广告增长 4.4%，CEM 消费者体验增长了 4.2%，但是 CRM 执行和支持上减少了 3.7%。欧洲增长最明显，其次是美国。</p><p line=\"7P3v\">Omnicom  CEO John Wren 表示拿下新业务后，应该对 2019 年的情况感到乐观。DDB 2018 年 11 月和美军签署了 10 年价值 40 亿美元的合同，OMD 2018 年 10 月在戴姆勒媒介评论业务中获胜。</p><p line=\"7P3v\" class=\"\">题图来自：<a href=\"https://unsplash.com/photos/W9kq9suABY4?utm_source=unsplash&amp;utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_content=creditCopyText\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Daniel Tseng</a> on <a href=\"https://unsplash.com/search/photos/japan?utm_source=unsplash&amp;utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_content=creditCopyText\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Unsplash</a></p>"}